l send the money to your account. You can cash out your money until the end of this month, after that you will not be able to cashout your money.","merge.closure.with_balance.heading":"Kleiderkreisel is closed. \u003cbr /\u003eYou have \u003cu\u003e{balance}\u003c/u\u003e in your account. Don’t lose it - withdraw it to your bank account.","merge.closure.without_balance.action":"Go to Vinted","merge.closure.without_balance.body":"Kleiderkreisel closed at the end of this year. To start buying and selling, you can join the Vinted community.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIn Vinted, you’ll find everything you need in one place. Sell your stuff quickly to a bigger community. Access the new Home category. Ship from just €0.99 (\u003chelp-link\u003eterms apply\u003c/help-link\u003e).","merge.closure.without_balance.heading":"Kleiderkreisel is closed. Go to \u003cu\u003eVinted\u003c/u\u003e to start buying and selling","merge.closure.without_balance.status.body":"You either didn’t have any money in Kleiderkreisel wallet or moved the money to Vinted. You’re ready to start selling and buying in Vinted!","merge.closure.without_balance.status.title":"You don’t have any money to cash out","merge.consent.confirmation_modal.actions.close":"OK, change selection","merge.consent.confirmation_modal.actions.continue":"Continue with current selection","merge.consent.confirmation_modal.body":"Bring everything you need with you to Vinted! You can’t move information later. Information you don’t choose to move will be deleted soon. ","merge.consent.confirmation_modal.title":"Select more information to improve your move","merge.consent.primary.balance_consent.note":"This data migration will last up to 48 hours","merge.consent.primary.balance_consent.title":"My funds, full name, date of birth, and address details","merge.consent.primary.body":"Your listings, reviews, followers, member description, profile picture, and forum posts/comments will be moved by clicking ‘Continue’.","merge.consent.primary.continue":"Continue","merge.consent.primary.more":"Learn more.","merge.consent.primary.no_consents_title":"Review the information we'll transfer for you:","merge.consent.primary.payments_consent.note":"This data migration will last up to 48 hours","merge.consent.primary.payments_consent.title":"My bank account number, full name, date of birth, first 6 and last 4 digits of card number, card expiry date, and address details","merge.consent.primary.shipping_consent.note":"","merge.consent.primary.shipping_consent.title":"My delivery options, shipping address, and shipping history","merge.consent.primary.title":"I agree to move the following account information:","merge.consent.secondary.body":"By checking the box above, you agree to move your listings, reviews, and followers from your Mamikreisel account.","merge.consent.secondary.continue":"Continue","merge.consent.secondary.migrate_linked.note":"","merge.consent.secondary.migrate_linked.title":"I agree to move my Mamikreisel account","merge.consent.secondary.more":"Learn more.","merge.consent.secondary.skip":"Skip","merge.consent.secondary.title":"Do you also want to move your Mamikreisel account information to Vinted?","merge.forum_banner.action":"Go to the new platform","merge.forum_banner.heading":"Vinted is growing","merge.forum_banner.text":"Get started on the new, improved Vinted to continue writing posts in the forum.\u003cbr/\u003eYou can no longer post here in the old forum.","merge.landing.faq.question_1.body":"Yes, we’ll take care of protecting your information and will move it in line with the GDPR.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eTo ensure that both Vinted platforms and all accounts, including yours, are safe from cyberattacks, unauthorised logins, and similar threats, we may use:\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ePhone number verification data\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAccount verification data\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eSuspicious activity data\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eBlocked member data\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\nFor more details, have a look at the paragraphs 2.3. and 2.4. of our \u003ca href=\"privacy-policy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ePrivacy Policy\u003c/a\u003e.","merge.landing.faq.question_1.title":"When can I move?","merge.landing.faq.question_2.body":"We’ll move your account along with these details:\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eListings\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eSaved searches\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eFavourites*\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eFollowers*\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eReviews\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eVouchers\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e“About me” text\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eProfile picture\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eName and surname\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eBirthdate\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n*\u003cstrong\u003eYour followers, favourites, as well as the member profiles you follow won’t appear\u003c/strong\u003e on the new Vinted until these members move their accounts and listings over. Also, for the same reason, some of your profile reviews can also be shown as anonymous for a while. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nBefore agreeing to move, you’ll also be able to choose whether or not to transfer:\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003ePersonal details and funds\u003c/b\u003e (full name, birthdate, address details, funds in your Vinted Balance)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003eYour payment details\u003c/b\u003e (bank account number, full name, billing address, first 6 and last 4 digits of the bank card, and card expiry date)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003eYour shipping details\u003c/b\u003e (delivery options, shipping address, shipping history)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e","merge.landing.faq.question_2.title":"What data can I transfer to the new app?","merge.landing.faq.question_3.body":"You’ll be able to contact members with whom you have unfinished orders till 30 April 2021 and complete these orders.","merge.landing.faq.question_3.title":"What if I still need to complete orders on the current app?","merge.landing.faq.question_4.body":"After you receive our invitation to move your account between 31 March - 1 April 2021, the actions that you can take on the old Vinted will be limited.  \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eFrom then on, you’ll only be able to:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eLog in to your old Vinted account\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eContact members with whom you have unfinished orders\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eContact us\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eWithdraw earnings to your bank account\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAgree to move your account over to the new Vinted\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\nPlease note that you won’t be able to start new orders, upload and favourite items, create forum posts, or do anything else that isn’t mentioned above. You’ll be able to do all these things on the new Vinted instead!","merge.landing.faq.question_4.title":"Can I still use this app after I’ve moved to the new one?","merge.landing.faq.question_5.body":"\u003cb\u003eWe’ll move\u003c/b\u003e your listings (unsold ones), saved searches, vouchers, “About me” text, profile picture, name and surname, birthdate, address and your saved shipping settings, bundle discounts, and your credit card data (full name, first 6 and last 4 digits of the bank card and card expiry date).\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eWe will also move selected forum threads that may include your posts. We will show these posts as anonymous until you move your account to the new Vinted.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eYour \u003cb\u003efollowers, followed members, and favourites\u003c/b\u003e will appear only when they move to the new Vinted. Until then, we may also show some of your reviews as anonymous.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cb\u003eWe won’t move\u003c/b\u003e the following information to the new platform:\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003eYour Vinted Balance\u003c/b\u003e (funds) — you will need to withdraw your funds to your bank account during the move. If some of your transactions are completed after the migration to the new platform, you can still withdraw those funds on the old platform.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003eYour identity (KYC) check\u003c/b\u003e — if you had completed an identity (KYC) check with our payment provider on the old platform, this information won’t be carried over, and you may be asked to redo it.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003eYour conversations\u003c/b\u003e with other members or us \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe statistics\u003c/b\u003e for your bumped items and Wardrobe Spotlight\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eWe won’t move the rest of the information from your account that wasn’t listed above.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eFor more information on how we will process your data, please see our \u003ca href=\"/privacy-policy\"\u003ePrivacy Policy\u003c/a\u003e.","merge.landing.faq.question_5.title":"Will all of my data move?","merge.landing.faq.question_6.body":"We will add a number to it as we move it. After that, you will be able to edit your username under your Profile \u003e Settings \u003e Profile details. Unfortunately, in such a case you won’t be able to use an identical username you’ve had before. Please note that the profile name change will be possible only if your username has been taken, and you will be able to change it only once.","merge.landing.faq.question_6.title":"What if my username on the united Vinted will be taken?","merge.landing.faq.question_7.body":"You will be able to choose whether to move your data from both accounts, or from a single one only.","merge.landing.faq.question_7.title":"What if I have 2 accounts: on the current Vinted and on Mūsų Mažyliai?","merge.minimal_consent.confirmation_modal.actions.all":"No, continue with all data","merge.minimal_consent.confirmation_modal.actions.minimal":"Yes, continue with minimum data","merge.minimal_consent.confirmation_modal.body":"You won’t be able to transfer any other information later. The data you choose not to move will eventually be deleted.","merge.minimal_consent.confirmation_modal.title":"Sure you only want to move minimum data?","merge.minimal_consent.simple.actions.continue":"Continue","merge.minimal_consent.simple.body":"To give you the best experience on the new version of Vinted, we’ll transfer all of your data, including listings, reviews, followers, member description and profile picture when you click ‘Continue’.  \u003ca href=\"/help\"\u003eLearn more\u003c/a\u003e","merge.minimal_consent.simple.title":"Transferring your account is simple","merge.minimal_consent.too_many_requests.actions.close":"Compris","merge.minimal_consent.too_many_requests.body":"Bear with us – there are lots of people moving their accounts right now. Close this message and tap ‘Continue with all data’ to try again. You’ll be able to move your account shortly. ","merge.minimal_consent.too_many_requests.title":"You’re in the queue to move your account","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.actions.continue":"Continue with all data","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.actions.minimal_continue":"Continue with minimum data","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.body":"We recommend transferring all of your data. This way you’ll be fully ready to start using the new version of our app.","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.data.all.balance":"Your funds, full name, date of birth, listings, reviews, followers, member description, and profile picture.\u2028","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.data.all.body":"\u003chelp-link\u003eLearn more\u003c/help-link\u003e","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.data.all.payments":"Bank account number, full holder name, first 6 and last 4 card number digits, card expiry date, billing address.\u2028","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.data.all.shipping":"Delivery options, shipping address, and shipping history.","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.data.all.title":"What does all data include?","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.data.minimal.body":"• Listings, reviews, followers, member description, and profile picture. \u003chelp-link\u003eLearn more\u003c/help-link\u003e","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.data.minimal.title":"What does minimum data include?","merge.minimal_consent.with_selection.title":"Take your account information with you","merge.missing_full_name.actions.submit":"Continue","merge.missing_full_name.body":"To use the new platform, you’ll need to provide us with your name. It will only be used to process payments, and won’t be shared with other members.","merge.missing_full_name.fields.real_name.errors.validate":"Il faut compléter ton nom et prénom ","merge.missing_full_name.fields.real_name.placeholder":"...","merge.missing_full_name.fields.real_name.title":"Nom et prénom","merge.missing_full_name.heading":"More information needed","merge.missing_user_information.actions.submit":"Continue","merge.missing_user_information.body":"Please provide the following information, so the new platform works for you. This will be used to process your payments and calculate applicable sales tax. It will not be publicly visible.","merge.missing_user_information.fields.name.errors.validate":"Il faut compléter ton nom et prénom ","merge.missing_user_information.fields.name.placeholder":"...","merge.missing_user_information.fields.name.title":"Nom et prénom","merge.missing_user_information.fields.postal_code.placeholder":"12345","merge.missing_user_information.fields.postal_code.title":"ZIP Code","merge.missing_user_information.heading":"Information needed","merge.pre_merge_hero_block.title":"Coming soon. Our new website will be up and running this October!","merge.single_account_consent.action":"Continue","merge.single_account_consent.body":"When you click ‘Continue’, we’ll move your most important data to the new app.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThis includes your listings, reviews, followers, member description, profile picture, full name, and date of birth.","merge.single_account_consent.title":"Bring your account with you","nationality_select.other_countries.title":"Autres pays","nationality_select.suggested_countries.title":"Suggéré d’après ton emplacement","native_country_names.at":"Österreich","native_country_names.be":"Belgique / België","native_country_names.ca":"Canada","native_country_names.cz":"Česká republika","native_country_names.de":"Deutschland","native_country_names.es":"España","native_country_names.fr":"France","native_country_names.hu":"Magyarország","native_country_names.it":"Italia","native_country_names.lt":"Lietuva","native_country_names.lu":"Luxembourg","native_country_names.nl":"Nederland","native_country_names.pl":"Polska","native_country_names.pt":"Portugal","native_country_names.ro":"România","native_country_names.se":"Konungariket Sverige","native_country_names.sk":"Slovenská republika","native_country_names.uk":"United Kingdom","native_country_names.us":"United States","net_promoter_score.open_question":"Facultatif : pourquoi as-tu mis cette note ?","net_promoter_score.question":"Recommanderiez-vous Vinted à vos amis ou collègues ?","net_promoter_score.score_explanation.likely_to_recommend":"Extrêmement probable","net_promoter_score.score_explanation.unlikely_to_recommend":"Pas du tout probable","net_promoter_score.submit":"Soumettre","new_badge":"Nouveau","new_payout.actions.add_account":"Ajouter un compte bancaire","new_payout.actions.payout":"Transférer","new_payout.error_modal.actions.close":"OK, fermer","new_payout.error_modal.title":"Désolé, une erreur s'est produite.","new_payout.note":"Le transfert vers ton compte bancaire peut prendre jusqu'à 5 jours ouvrés.","new_payout.title":"Montant","newsletter.banner.dismiss":"Non merci","newsletter.banner.subscribe":